title: *PATREON PREVIEW* 2 Innocent 2 Gay
description:
We do solemnly swear that we will support and defend the Throw Gang against all enemies, foreign and domestic. Historic weeks call for historic pods and Jimmy and Larry are ready to lead by example as they break down Inauguration Day, the politics of political fashion, neoliberal bangers, Trump’s pardons at the buzzer, Drake’s delay, the NBA’s vaccination plan, Gwyneth Paltrow’s exploding vagina candle, Travis Scott’s  evil McNugget pillows, hits and misses from Raf for Prada, Virgil for LV, Rick for Converse and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
